{"id":1698080,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-19T14:14:58.948Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":20000,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://a-desk.org/magazine/enviromelisma/","id":1698080,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["ES"],"original_language":"es","original_title":"Environmelisma","overview":"The entire project examines three interconnected extractivist processes in that area of southeastern Spain: mining in La Unión, construction in La Manga, and agroindustry in the Mar Menor. This short film was scripted as a spiral, revisiting the same three locations in three rounds. It overlaps archival materials with new recordings, aiming to approach the territory as a stratified archival ground – a form of storytelling conveyed by the land and water themselves. The archival materials are treated as compacted strata, whose grain and texture offer the possibility of excavating the trauma inscribed in the territory.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/8BT1wg6L0UVPcLQnsxjQVsKmMZa.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":296503,"logo_path":null,"name":"Sensor Projects","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"ES","name":"Spain"}],"release_date":"2025-11-22","revenue":0,"runtime":10,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"No Language","iso_639_1":"xx","name":"No Language"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Environmelisma","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1193181,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Pedro André","original_name":"Pedro André","popularity":0.0518,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"6a0b7f0234606da65caafdc7","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6168187,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Lorenzo Sandoval","original_name":"Lorenzo Sandoval","popularity":0.0168,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"6a0b7f13155696b756